ote><br />\n<br />\n有,老豆度有我既房但好少番去  同佢地兩個關係都唔算好</blockquote><br />\n佢地都有左自己家庭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你會唔會去拜下年呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講,真係唔知老豆係大陸有冇.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老母就差D有,不過結唔成<br />\n<br />\n老實講我都唔想佢地再搞個家庭出黎<br />\n<br />\n搞得衰&gt;&gt;我會心諗:屌又去害9人<br />\n搞得好&gt;&gt;我會唔開心:既然你地有能力 咁你地做乜9唔理我?"},{"pid":"168851e8dc7629be96b6e5f7bdd6a19fc623c7bd","tid":97281,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"這裏是拉登 這裏有力量"},{"pid":"24f541383af0c118381444780c53e32400e405f7","tid":97281,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打唔好傷心<br />\n呢度應該好多人陪你<br />\n我細個都係寄養係人地屋企大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寄養家庭對你好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會諗住報答番佢地？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今晚就係去左佢地屋企團年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記得對佢地好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得親生既就話生左你出黎好好醜醜都應該養大埋你<br />\n而養父母比飯你食就真係無條件既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762e25f8cb2e6733c7fe37dd895aacc2013a19ca","tid":97281,"uid":6427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信父母都仲好錫你 唔好傷心"},{"pid":"464704ebcd0a0b12a0c279690da03b8e340ff573","tid":97281,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有,老豆度有我既房但好少番去  同佢地兩個關係都唔算好</blockquote><br />\n佢地都有左自己家庭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你會唔會去拜下年呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講,真係唔知老豆係大陸有冇.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老母就差D有,不過結唔成<br />\n<br />\n老實講我都唔想佢地再搞個家庭出黎<br />\n<br />\n搞得衰&amp;gt;&amp;gt;我會心諗:屌又去害9人<br />\n搞得好&amp;gt;&amp;gt;我會唔開心:既然你地有能力 咁你地做乜9唔理我?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明你諗法<br />\n不過你爸爸同媽媽之間唔work係佢兩個唔夾 又無諗清楚就生b<br />\n唔係話有能力就一定work既"},{"pid":"b54249203d1017eab567c26dd4a60df215432876","tid":97281,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"有時我都羨慕人地同老豆老母關係好，唔差又唔好，無交流咁濟"},{"pid":"d766852300dbf0223f47be6d16bd8a368a284645","tid":97281,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"冇咩親戚但一家人好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82e5b166839cedd8f6e435d4747a68302cb0fe6","tid":97281,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:26:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寄養家庭對你好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會諗住報答番佢地？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今晚就係去左佢地屋企團年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記得對佢地好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得親生既就話生左你出黎好好醜醜都應該養大埋你<br />\n而養父母比飯你食就真係無條件既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係我老豆賭到差人好多錢走左佬<br />\n老母又養唔掂我兩兄弟咪放我係親戚度<br />\n我都好感謝佢地係我最無依無靠既時候收留左我<br />\n不過寄人籬下點都會唔開心<br />\n雖然佢地對我好好但同佢啲仔女比始終都唔同"},{"pid":"2c5e082f5f039fd73d6b0ea987ab0cbec4f770f1","tid":97281,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有,老豆度有我既房但好少番去  同佢地兩個關係都唔算好</blockquote><br />\n佢地都有左自己家庭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你會唔會去拜下年呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講,真係唔知老豆係大陸有冇.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老母就差D有,不過結唔成<br />\n<br />\n老實講我都唔想佢地再搞個家庭出黎<br />\n<br />\n搞得衰&amp;gt;&amp;gt;我會心諗:屌又去害9人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">搞得好&amp;gt;&amp;gt;我會唔開心:既然你地有能力 咁你地做乜9唔理我</span>?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know the feeling <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f465b016b942ca304b74d89ac0bd3fbca2954a6","tid":97281,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"同爸媽關係超好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地又錫我，想食乜就煮乜，一齊買野煮飯，唔夠錢開句聲就有，不過我通常唔會要錢，唔想加重佢地負擔，阿哥又錫我，成日不齊傾心事，大時大節就會有啲應節活動搞，例如一家人一齊包傻，整油角，寫揮春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主唔洗咁灰，找對的人，組織你要既家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4d0de02d5fdb5855f08a58bc6d03e8699a67dd","tid":97281,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信父母都仲好錫你 唔好傷心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年佢地離婚判撫養權好似扔燙手山芋咁左扔右扔 <br />\n後尾又日日放工都當我出氣袋咁鬧 咁多年同佢地兩個都係鬧交多過正常交流<br />\n又話我既存在係阻住佢地 <br />\n<br />\n宜家就算錫番我我都會覺得係有目的既,就係自己老喇想有人養"},{"pid":"4a4d582bc8fcc810c936c3be40cd22c6ee736735","tid":97281,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"頂9住啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c917b53b2d50efb38e377cdf3a980004e499e69","tid":97281,"uid":29592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加住係男朋友屋企但新年唔會帶埋我<br />\n年年既呢個時候都無節目又唔知去邊<br />\n更加無朋友得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d45d024468b365ff2c96b6eea5b0f4ca6cfc1c","tid":97281,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信父母都仲好錫你 唔好傷心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年佢地離婚判撫養權好似扔燙手山芋咁左扔右扔 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後尾又日日放工都當我出氣袋咁鬧</span> 咁多年同佢地兩個都係鬧交多過正常交流<br />\n又話我既存在係阻住佢地 <br />\n<br />\n宜家就算錫番我我都會覺得係有目的既,就係自己老喇想有人養</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得罪講句 好撚仆街"},{"pid":"33871c604de153dbb85137814d943fc9081e46ef","tid":97281,"uid":31712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"都係一個人外國過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  男朋友做野又夜返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e3c87a07fa72ccf2a14b9c20709f8b12eb2991","tid":97281,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"巴打做個真漢子啦，大時大節感觸下好正常，之後識企番起身就得，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}